<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Terms governing the use of the ASM Investments website."
>
  <SectionContainer bg="cream">
    <Prose>
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="!mt-2 text-small text-muted">Last updated: 31 May 2026 · Draft pending legal review</p>

      <p>
        These terms govern your use of the ASM Investments website at asmfinance.in (the “site”). By
        using the site, you agree to them. If you do not agree, please do not use the site.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Nature of this site</h2>
      <p>
        This site is informational. It describes who we are and the services we offer as an
        AMFI-registered mutual fund distributor and IRDAI point-of-sale person. Nothing on the site
        is an offer, solicitation, or recommendation to buy or sell any security or financial
        product.
      </p>

      <h2>2. No investment advice through the site</h2>
      <p>
        We do not provide investment, tax, legal or financial advice through this site. Any
        engagement begins only after a direct conversation, suitability assessment, and the
        applicable onboarding and documentation. Investments in securities and mutual funds are
        subject to market risks; please read all scheme-related documents carefully.
