      <h2>4. External links</h2>
      <p>
        The site may link to third-party websites and tools (for example, a calendar booking
        service). We are not responsible for their content, availability, or privacy practices.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        The ASM Investments name, wordmark, content, and design are our property or used with
        permission. You may not reproduce them without our written consent.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Governing law and jurisdiction</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of India. The courts at Mathura, Uttar Pradesh have
        exclusive jurisdiction over any dispute relating to the site.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these terms from time to time. The “last updated” date above reflects the latest version.</p>

      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:hello@asmfinance.in">hello@asmfinance.in</a>.
      </p>
    </Prose>
